history.content:
Keep in mind that I do not have access to the student side of enrollments so another student may be better qualified to respond to this question.

From what I have been told, you input the permission number when you're first selecting the class - it should be a box near the checkbox to waitlist for a class. Do this BEFORE you add to the shopping cart.
